<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Apresentação TCC: Tecnologias de Software em Fonoaudiologia</title>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Paleta de Cores Profissional */
            --primary: #1e3c72;    /* Azul Profundo */
            --secondary: #2a5298;  /* Azul Vibrante */
            --accent: #00b09b;     /* Verde Tiffanys/Teal */
            --light: #f0f2f5;      /* Cinza Muito Claro */
            --dark: #2d3436;       /* Grafite */
            --white: #ffffff;
            --warning: #f1c40f;
            --danger: #e74c3c;
            --success: #27ae60;
            --border: #dfe6e9;
            --card-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            --transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .container {
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        /* --- SIDEBAR --- */
        .sidebar {
            width: 280px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary) 0%, #102040 100%);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            position: fixed;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 4px 0 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .sidebar-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        
        .sidebar-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .nav-menu { list-style: none; }
        .nav-section-title {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            margin: 25px 0 10px 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .nav-item {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin: 6px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
        }
        
        .nav-item:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateX(4px);
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .nav-item.active {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), transparent);
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: -4px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .nav-subitem {
            padding-left: 42px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            border-left: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
        }

        /* --- MAIN CONTENT --- */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            margin-left: 280px;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        
        .slide {
            display: none;
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            padding: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            min-height: 90vh;
            animation: fadeInSlide 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Top Gradient Border */
        .slide::after {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), var(--accent));
        }
        
        .slide.active { display: block; }

        /* --- TYPOGRAPHY & HEADERS --- */
        .slide-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light);
        }
        
        .slide-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 800;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(0deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        h3.section-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin: 40px 0 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        /* --- CARDS & LAYOUTS --- */
        .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 25px; }
        .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
        .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }

        .content-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .content-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: rgba(42, 82, 152, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* --- ELEMENTOS VISUAIS NOVOS --- */
        
        /* 1. Donut Chart (CSS Only) */
        .chart-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            background: #f8fbff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #e1e8f0;
        }
        .donut-chart {
            width: 100px; height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: conic-gradient(var(--accent) 0% 40%, #e0e0e0 40% 100%);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .donut-inner {
            width: 70px; height: 70px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        /* 2. Timeline Vertical */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .timeline::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 3px;
            background: var(--border); border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative; margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute; left: -36px; top: 0;
            width: 15px; height: 15px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            border: 3px solid var(--white);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--secondary);
        }
        
        /* 3. Badges */
        .badge-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .badge {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #eef2f7;
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 1px solid #dce4ec;
        }
        .badge.accent { background: rgba(0, 176, 155, 0.1); color: var(--accent); border-color: rgba(0, 176, 155, 0.2); }

        /* 4. Progress/Skill Bars */
        .skill-bar-container { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .skill-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .skill-track { width: 100%; height: 8px; background: #eee; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
        .skill-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; animation: fillBar 1.5s ease-out forwards; }
        
        /* 5. Comparison Cards (Green/Red) */
        .comparison-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .comp-card { padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 5px solid; }
        .comp-card.pros { background: #f0f9eb; border-color: var(--success); }
        .comp-card.cons { background: #fdf0ed; border-color: var(--danger); }
        .comp-title { font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }

        /* 6. Quote Block */
        .quote-block {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            position: relative;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.2);
        }
        .quote-block::before {
            content: '"'; font-size: 5rem; position: absolute; top: -10px; left: 10px; opacity: 0.2; font-family: serif;
        }

        /* 7. Flowchart Visual (CSS Only) */
        .flow-diagram {
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
        }
        .flow-box {
            background: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center; width: 80%; max-width: 400px;
            font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark);
            position: relative;
        }
        .flow-box.start { background: var(--primary); color: white; border: none; }
        .flow-box.end { background: var(--accent); color: white; border: none; }
        .flow-arrow { color: #bdc3c7; }

        /* --- SLIDE COVER --- */
        .slide-cover {
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center; min-height: 80vh; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        /* Dynamic Background Circles */
        .bg-circle {
            position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.05; z-index: 0;
        }
        .c1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: var(--secondary); top: -100px; left: -100px; }
        .c2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: var(--accent); bottom: -50px; right: -50px; }
        .c3 { width: 150px; height: 150px; border: 20px solid var(--primary); top: 20%; right: 10%; }

        .cover-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        .cover-icon-lg {
            width: 100px; height: 100px; background: rgba(42, 82, 152, 0.05);
            border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px; color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        /* --- NAVIGATION CONTROLS --- */
        .nav-controls {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 50px; padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; z-index: 10;
        }
        .btn-nav {
            padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 30px; border: none; cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-prev { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--dark); }
        .btn-prev:hover { background: #f8f9fa; transform: translateX(-5px); }
        
        .btn-next { background: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.3); }
        .btn-next:hover { background: var(--secondary); transform: translateX(5px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(30, 60, 114, 0.4); }
        
        .btn-nav:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none !important; box-shadow: none !important; }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInSlide { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes fillBar { from { width: 0; } }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .sidebar { width: 70px; padding: 20px 10px; }
            .sidebar-header h2 span, .sidebar-header p, .nav-section-title, .nav-item span, .nav-subitem { display: none; }
            .main-content { margin-left: 70px; padding: 20px; }
            .nav-item { justify-content: center; }
            .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <i data-lucide="cpu" size="32" color="#00b09b"></i>
                <h2><span>Tecno</span>Fono</h2>
                <p>TCC 2025</p>
            </div>
            
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <div class="nav-section-title">Principal</div>
                <li class="nav-item active" data-slide="0">
                    <i data-lucide="home"></i> <span>Capa</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="1">
                    <i data-lucide="info"></i> <span>1. Introdução</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="2">
                    <i data-lucide="book-open"></i> <span>2. Fundamentação</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="3">
                    <i data-lucide="crosshair"></i> <span>3. Objetivos</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="4">
                    <i data-lucide="search"></i> <span>4. Metodologia</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="5">
                    <i data-lucide="bar-chart-2"></i> <span>5. Resultados</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="6">
                    <i data-lucide="check-circle"></i> <span>6. Conclusão</span>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" data-slide="7">
                    <i data-lucide="file-text"></i> <span>7. Referências</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">

            <div class="slide active" id="slide-0">
                <div class="slide-cover">
                    <div class="bg-circle c1"></div>
                    <div class="bg-circle c2"></div>
                    <div class="bg-circle c3"></div>
                    
                    <div class="cover-content">
                        <div class="cover-icon-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="monitor-smartphone" size="48"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.2;">
                            O USO DE TECNOLOGIAS DE SOFTWARE <br> EM TERAPIA FONOAUDIOLÓGICA
                        </h1>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--secondary); letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                            REVISÃO DE LITERATURA
                        </h3>
                        
                        <div style="background: white; padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: inline-block;">
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--dark);"><strong>Autora:</strong> Giullia Ferreira Rodrigues</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--dark);"><strong>Orientadora:</strong> Profa. Dra. Thais Antonelli Diniz Hein</p>
                            <hr style="margin: 15px 0; border-color: #eee;">
                            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #777;">
                                PONTIFÍCIA UNIVERSIDADE CATÓLICA DE CAMPINAS<br>
                                ESCOLA DE CIÊNCIAS DA VIDA • FACULDADE DE FONOAUDIOLOGIA<br>
                                2025
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-controls">
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-prev" disabled>Anterior</button>
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-next">Começar <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="slide" id="slide-1">
                <div class="slide-header">
                    <i data-lucide="info" size="32" color="#2a5298"></i>
                    <h2>1. INTRODUÇÃO</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div>
                        <div class="content-card" style="height: 100%;">
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">Contextualização</h4>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                A Fonoaudiologia estuda a comunicação humana e suas alterações. A integração de recursos tecnológicos é um fenômeno em expansão, visando otimizar capacidades funcionais e qualidade de vida.
                            </p>
                            <div class="badge-container">
                                <span class="badge accent">Inovação</span>
                                <span class="badge">Qualidade de Vida</span>
                                <span class="badge">Digitalização</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <div class="chart-container">
                            <div class="donut-chart">
                                <div class="donut-inner">40%</div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h5 style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px;">Alta Demanda</h5>
                                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;">
                                    Distúrbios dos Sons da Fala (DSF) constituem mais de 40% da casuística clínica, justificando o uso de softwares de apoio.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="content-card" style="margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warning);">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" color="#f1c40f"></i>
                                <h4 style="color: var(--dark);">Impacto da COVID-19</h4>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                                A pandemia acelerou drasticamente a <strong>Telefonoaudiologia</strong>, superando barreiras geográficas e consolidando práticas híbridas.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="content-card" style="margin-top: 25px; background: #fff5f5; border-color: #fed7d7;">
                    <h4 style="color: var(--danger); margin-bottom: 10px;">O Problema de Pesquisa</h4>
                    <p>Apesar do potencial, persiste uma <strong>carência de estudos sistematizados</strong> sobre a efetiva prevalência, padrões de uso e validação clínica dessas inovações.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="nav-controls">
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-prev"><i data-lucide="arrow-left"></i> Anterior</button>
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-next">Próximo <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
                <div class="slide-header">
                    <i data-lucide="book-open" size="32" color="#2a5298"></i>
                    <h2>2. FUNDAMENTAÇÃO TEÓRICA</h2>
                </div>

                <h3 class="section-title">Categorias de Tecnologias de Software</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">A revisão categoriza o uso de softwares em duas vertentes principais:</p>

                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div class="content-card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i data-lucide="settings"></i></div>
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">1. Avaliação Diagnóstica</h4>
                        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Análise acústica da voz (F0, Jitter, Shimmer).
                            </li>
                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Audiômetros computadorizados.
                            </li>
                            <li style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Mapeamento de AASI/Implante Coclear.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i data-lucide="play-circle"></i></div>
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">2. Intervenção Terapêutica</h4>
                        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Treino auditivo-cognitivo.
                            </li>
                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Biofeedback visual de fala.
                            </li>
                            <li style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                                <i data-lucide="check" size="16" color="var(--success)"></i> Gamificação (ex: Wordwall, GameFono).
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="content-card" style="margin-top: 30px; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 5px;">Democratização via Tecnologia Assistiva (TA)</h4>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">Aplicativos móveis tornaram a <strong>Comunicação Aumentativa e Alternativa (CAA)</strong> acessível, substituindo hardwares caros.</p>
                        </div>
                        <i data-lucide="smartphone" size="40" color="var(--accent)" style="opacity: 0.5;"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="nav-controls">
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-prev"><i data-lucide="arrow-left"></i> Anterior</button>
                    <button class="btn-nav btn-next">Próximo <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="slide" id="slide-3">
                <div class="slide-header">
                    <i data-lucide="crosshair" size="32" color="#2a5298"></i>
                    <h2>3. OBJETIVOS</h2>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                    <div style="display: inline-block; background: #eef4ff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #d0e1fd;">
                        <h5 style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 10px;">Objetivo Geral</h5>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); max-width: 600px;">
                            Analisar a incidência e o contexto de utilização de tecnologias de software na prática da terapia fonoaudiológica.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="section-title">Objetivos Específicos</h3>
                <div class="grid-3">
                    <div class="content-card" style="text-align: center;">
                        <div class="card-icon" style="margin: 0 auto 15px;"><i data-lucide="search"></i></div>
                        <strong>Identificar Tipos</strong>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 10px; color: #666;">Quais softwares são mais empregados pelos profissionais.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content-card" style="text-align: center;">
